data.comment: The big names in today's match at Central Stadium have now been confirmed.
Today's referee, Pavel Kukuyan, has blown to start the match.
In the minute 1, Pavel Kukuyan awards the home team a throw-in.
Throw-in Spartak Moscow.
Ural Yekaterinburg awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 2, Pavel Kukuyan signals a throw-in for Spartak Moscow, close to Ural Yekaterinburg's area.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a free kick to Spartak Moscow in their own half.
Aleksandr Sobolev of Spartak Moscow smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
In the minute 3, Pavel Kukuyan signals a free kick to Ural Yekaterinburg.
Ural Yekaterinburg have been awarded a corner by Pavel Kukuyan.
Corner awarded to Ural Yekaterinburg.
In the minute 6, Goal! Aleksandr Sobolev gives Spartak Moscow a 0-1 lead in Ekaterinburg.
Ayrton Lucas with an assist there.
Throw-in for Spartak Moscow in their own half.
In the minute 8, Free kick Ural Yekaterinburg.
In Ekaterinburg a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Ball safe as Ural Yekaterinburg is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 10, Ural Yekaterinburg are pushing forward but Eric Bicfalvi's finish is wide of the goal.
Pavel Kukuyan awards Spartak Moscow a goal kick.
Throw-in for Ural Yekaterinburg in the half of Spartak Moscow.
In the minute 10, Throw-in for Ural Yekaterinburg close to the penalty box.
Ural Yekaterinburg have been awarded a corner by Pavel Kukuyan.
Pogrebnyak Pavel scores with his head for Ural Yekaterinburg to level the match at 1-1.
In the minute 11, Great play from Othman El Kabir to set up the goal.
Free kick for Ural Yekaterinburg in their own half.
Throw-in for Ural Yekaterinburg at Central Stadium.
In the minute 13, Pavel Kukuyan awards the home team a throw-in.
Spartak Moscow awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Ball safe as Spartak Moscow is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 15, Ural Yekaterinburg have a goal kick.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a Ural Yekaterinburg throw-in in Spartak Moscow's half.
Denys Kulakov (Ural Yekaterinburg) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 17, Corner awarded to Ural Yekaterinburg.
Spartak Moscow awarded a free kick in their own half.
Free kick for Spartak Moscow in the half of Ural Yekaterinburg.
In the minute 20, Throw-in for Ural Yekaterinburg at Central Stadium.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a free kick to Ural Yekaterinburg in their own half.
In the minute 23, Throw-in for Ural Yekaterinburg in their own half.
Alex Kral (Spartak Moscow) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
Corner awarded to Ural Yekaterinburg.
In the minute 25, Throw-in Spartak Moscow.
Ural Yekaterinburg awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Ural Yekaterinburg to take a throw-in in Spartak Moscow territory.
In the minute 26, Ural Yekaterinburg have a dangerous throw-in.
Ural Yekaterinburg's Eric Bicfalvi misses with an attempt on goal.
Important block from the Spartak Moscow defence as Andrey Egorychev fires in a strike for Ural Yekaterinburg.
In the minute 31, Throw-in high up the field for Ural Yekaterinburg in Ekaterinburg.
Throw-in for Spartak Moscow in their own half.
Pavel Kukuyan awards the away team a throw-in.
In the minute 33, Free kick for Ural Yekaterinburg in their own half.
Free kick for Ural Yekaterinburg in the half of Spartak Moscow.
In the minute 34, Pavel Kukuyan signals a free kick to Ural Yekaterinburg.
Victor Moses (Spartak Moscow) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
Ural Yekaterinburg awarded a free kick in their own half.
Spartak Moscow awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 37, Can Ural Yekaterinburg get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Spartak Moscow's half?
Ural Yekaterinburg needs to be cautious. Spartak Moscow have an attacking throw-in.
It's getting dangerous! Free kick for Spartak Moscow close to the penalty box.
In the minute 39, Spartak Moscow have been awarded a corner by Pavel Kukuyan.
Spartak Moscow attack but Aleksandr Sobolev's header doesn't find the target.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Ekaterinburg.
In the minute 41, Can Ural Yekaterinburg capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Spartak Moscow's half?
Georgi Dzhikiya (Spartak Moscow) wins the ball in the air but heads wide.
Goal kick for Ural Yekaterinburg at Central Stadium.
In the minute 44, Ural Yekaterinburg push forward at Central Stadium and Eric Bicfalvi gets in a great header. The attempt is cleared by the Spartak Moscow defence.
Free kick for Spartak Moscow in their own half.
Othman El Kabir (Ural Yekaterinburg) has received a yellow card from Pavel Kukuyan.
In the minute 45, An attacking Spartak Moscow player has been brought down in the area ... It's a penalty!
In the minute 45, Pavel Kukuyan will wait an extra 1 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 1st half.
The first-half has ended.
Ural Yekaterinburg's Vladimir Rykov has been booked in Ekaterinburg.
Goal! Spartak Moscow take a 1-2 lead thanks to a Aleksandr Sobolev spot-kick..
The second-half is underway in Ekaterinburg.
Spartak Moscow to take a throw-in in Ural Yekaterinburg territory.
In the minute 46, Nail Umyarov is replacing Victor Moses for the away team.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a free kick to Ural Yekaterinburg in their own half.
In the minute 48, A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Can Spartak Moscow capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Ural Yekaterinburg's half?
Ball safe as Ural Yekaterinburg is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In the minute 49, Throw-in Spartak Moscow.
Throw-in for Ural Yekaterinburg at Central Stadium.
Throw-in Spartak Moscow.
In the minute 50, In Ekaterinburg a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Pavel Kukuyan awards Spartak Moscow a goal kick.
Spartak Moscow awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 53, Ural Yekaterinburg will need to be alert as they defend a dangerous free kick from Spartak Moscow.
Nikolay Zolotov (Ural Yekaterinburg) has received a first yellow card.
Spartak Moscow surge into the attack at Central Stadium but Samuel Gigotâ€™s header is off-target.
In the minute 54, Ural Yekaterinburg have a goal kick.
Free kick Spartak Moscow.
Free kick for Ural Yekaterinburg in their own half.
In the minute 57, Spartak Moscow pushes forward through Ezequiel Ponce, whose finish on goal is saved.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a free kick to Ural Yekaterinburg in their own half.
Goal! The home team draw level at 2-2 through Rafal Augustyniak.
In the minute 62, Spartak Moscow have been awarded a corner by Pavel Kukuyan.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a free kick to Spartak Moscow.
Throw-in for Spartak Moscow in the half of Ural Yekaterinburg.
In the minute 63, In Ekaterinburg a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Corner awarded to Ural Yekaterinburg.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a Spartak Moscow throw-in in Ural Yekaterinburg's half.
In the minute 67, Spartak Moscow have been awarded a corner by Pavel Kukuyan.
Spartak Moscow drives forward and Ayrton Lucas gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
Can Ural Yekaterinburg get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Spartak Moscow's half?
In the minute 68, Andrey Egorychev (Ural Yekaterinburg) is first to the ball but his header is off-target.
Ball goes out of play for a Spartak Moscow goal kick.
Throw-in for Spartak Moscow in their own half.
In the minute 69, Pavel Kukuyan signals a free kick to Spartak Moscow in their own half.
Spartak Moscow push forward at Central Stadium and Roman Zobnin gets in a strike. This is blocked, however, by a determined Ural Yekaterinburg defence.
Spartak Moscow's Roman Zobnin gets in a shot but it is blocked by a Ural Yekaterinburg defender.
In the minute 70, Corner awarded to Spartak Moscow.
Throw-in for Spartak Moscow close to the penalty box.
Free kick for Ural Yekaterinburg in their own half.
In the minute 72, Throw-in for Ural Yekaterinburg in the half of Spartak Moscow.
Can Spartak Moscow capitalize from this dangerous free kick?
Spartak Moscow drive upfield and Aleksandr Sobolev gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Ural Yekaterinburg defender.
In the minute 75, Corner awarded to Spartak Moscow.
Ural Yekaterinburg needs to be cautious. Spartak Moscow have an attacking throw-in.
Spartak Moscow have a dangerous throw-in.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a throw-in for Spartak Moscow, close to Ural Yekaterinburg's area.
In the minute 78, Yuriy Matveev is making the team's first substitution at Central Stadium with Dmitri Efremov replacing Othman El Kabir.
Can Spartak Moscow get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Ural Yekaterinburg's half?
In the minute 80, Spartak Moscow's Nail Umyarov is on target but unsuccessful.
Spartak Moscow have been awarded a corner by Pavel Kukuyan.
Aleksandr Sobolev (Spartak Moscow) gets up for a header but cannot keep the ball on target.
In the minute 80, It's a goal kick for the home team in Ekaterinburg.
Spartak Moscow awarded a free kick in their own half.
Ural Yekaterinburg are in shooting range from this free kick.
The away team have replaced Ezequiel Ponce with Aleksandr Kokorin. This is the second substitution made today by Domenico Tedesco.
In the minute 82, Danijel Miskic is replacing Branko Jovicic for Ural Yekaterinburg at Central Stadium.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a free kick to Ural Yekaterinburg in their own half.
In the minute 85, Spartak Moscow awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Pavel Kukuyan waits before resuming play because Eric Bicfalvi for Ural Yekaterinburg is still down.
In the minute 86, Eric Bicfalvi has recovered and rejoins the match in Ekaterinburg.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a free kick to Ural Yekaterinburg just outside Spartak Moscow's area.
At Central Stadium, Ayrton Lucas has been yellow-carded for the away team.
Pavel Kukuyan signals a Spartak Moscow throw-in in Ural Yekaterinburg's half.
In the minute 88, Spartak Moscow's Aleksandr Sobolev goes close with his head but his effort is blocked.
Free kick for Ural Yekaterinburg in the half of Spartak Moscow.
Samuel Gigot for Spartak Moscow has been booked by Pavel Kukuyan and receives a first yellow card.
In the minute 89, Zelimkhan Bakaev is on a sub for Aleksandr Sobolev for Spartak Moscow.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Corner awarded to Ural Yekaterinburg.
3 minutes of injury time will be added to the 2nd half.
At Central Stadium, Ural Yekaterinburg are penalized for being offside.
Zelimkhan Bakaev gets his shot on target but fails to score for Spartak Moscow.
Spartak Moscow to take a throw-in in Ural Yekaterinburg territory.
The second-half is over. The match ends 2-2.
